

== Set up single-installation-mode ==

-- Create a MySQL database, restore the sql dumps in doc/sql --

cat doc/sql/structure.sql | mysql -u root -p insights_github
cat doc/sql/master.sql    | mysql -u root -p insights_github
cat doc/sql/basedata.sql  | mysql -u root -p insights_github

basedata.sql contains settings,
- base__user-table, contains a default 'admin' user with password 'test123'. The application hashes passwords by default, but plain-text is also supported 
- insights__customer-table, insights supports a multi-user/multi-database set-up. This table contains the databasename 'insights_github'. If you choose another database, change the value of the insights__customer.databaseName-column


-- Configure, copy config/config-sample.php to config/config-local.php --

Read the instructions in the Php-file

